<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-ca645f178faddcb25313d1c9b9d2a93a77b4c8a4">Horn of Rohan (+2)</h2>
<em>A horn carved from the bones of the Dragon of Ered-Mithrin, this heirloom of the House of Eorl bestows to its user the gifts of courage and command.</em> <p>
It can be activated for heroism, berserker, haste every 250 turns if it is being worn. It increases your wisdom and charisma by 2. It allows you to sense the presence of dragons. It cannot be harmed by acid, cold, lightning or fire. 
</p>
